Package: aigtheme
Title: MAKING GGPLOT GRAPHICS FOLLOWING AI GROUP STYLE GUIDE
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Andrew", "Bridger", email = "andrewjohnbridger@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helps create and export ggplot2 charts in the style used by 
    the Ai Group thanks to two useful functions, one for styling and another for exporting ggplot graphics. Code is based off bbplot from the BBC
